Marcus Chen had been a veterinary technician for 8 years when the idea hit him: what if pet owners could get grooming, walking, and basic health advice through one AI-powered app?

He typed his idea into InstantCompany and within 60 seconds had a brand name, domain, pricing model, and full landing page copy. Two days later, PetPal AI was live.

"I went from a napkin idea to a fully branded business in under a minute," says Marcus. "The positioning statement alone would have taken me a week to write on my own."

Within three months, PetPal AI had 2,000 monthly active users and had secured its first round of angel funding.
